OL,3,C'More mental health drop-in centres
OL,4,Cneeded' as Welsh Government launch
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FYoung people say drop in centres could
OL,8,Fhelp long waits for mental health
OL,9,Fsupport.
OL,11,FThe has opened up a new policy for
OL,12,Fconsultation on , suicide, and self
OL,13,Fharm.
OL,15,FPart of that policy would be more
OL,16,Fcommunity support to help people
OL,17,Foutside of a clinical setting - like
OL,18,FThe Hangout, a drop-in centre for
OL,19,Fyoung people in Cardiff.
