OL,3,C'More mental health drop-in centres
OL,4,Cneeded' as Welsh Government launch
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FOne regular attendee at the centre is
OL,8,FAiyan. The 16-year-old says the
OL,9,FHangout has "a sense of belonging to a
OL,10,Fcommunity that is composed of other
OL,11,Fyoung people who are suffering from
OL,12,Fother similar situations".
OL,14,FLana was referred to the Hangout by
OL,15,Fmental health services. She agrees
OL,16,Fthat there's a sense of "community
OL,17,Fthat's been cultivated" by both staff
OL,18,Fand users of the service.
