OL,3,C'More mental health drop-in centres
OL,4,Cneeded' as Welsh Government launch
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,F"Everyone's really friendly and
OL,8,Faccepting. We're all on the same page,
OL,9,Fwe all have our struggles, so it
OL,10,Fcreates a really non judgemental safe
OL,11,Fspace," she said.
OL,13,FIt's hoped that more schemes like this
OL,14,Fcould help tackle the long waiting
OL,15,Flists to see a mental health
OL,16,Fprofessional.
OL,18,FLatest figures suggest more than a
OL,19,Fthird of children on the CAMHS waiting
OL,20,Flists are waiting over a month to see
OL,21,Fsomeone.
