OL,3,C'More mental health drop-in centres
OL,4,Cneeded' as Welsh Government launch
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FLong waits for help are something that
OL,8,FLana says that she has experienced.
OL,10,F"I could have really benefitted from a
OL,11,Fplace like this for a long time and I
OL,12,Fonly recently learnt about it and it's
OL,13,Fbeen great," she said.
OL,15,FJen Love, who manages The Hangout says
OL,16,Fit's something she'd like to see "in
OL,17,Fevery single community".
