OL,3,C'More mental health drop-in centres
OL,4,Cneeded' as Welsh Government launch
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FShe added: "Whether that looks like
OL,8,Fevery town every city, or even more in
OL,9,FCardiff, that would be amazing, but I
OL,10,Fthink the open access drop in model is
OL,11,Fexactly where we need to go."
OL,13,FHalf of mental health conditions have
OL,14,Fimpacted people by the age of 14 and
OL,15,F75% by the age of 23, something the
OL,16,FWelsh Government says can be prevented
OL,17,Fby "ensuring everyone has equal access
OL,18,Fto the things they need to maintain
OL,19,Fgood mental health, like exercise, the
OL,20,Fnatural environment and belonging to
OL,21,Fthe community".
