OL,7,FLynne Neagle, deputy minister for
OL,8,Fmental health and wellbeing, said that
OL,9,Fthe Hangout is an "innovative approach
OL,10,Fto providing trauma informed and
OL,11,Fcompassionate support for young people
OL,12,Fin a safe and comfortable environment".
OL,14,FThe consultation closes on the 11 June.
